      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;abu-l-qāsim-ʿubayd-allāh-b-ʿabd-allāh-ibn-khurdādhbih-ca-820825912-ابوالقاسم-عبیدالله-عبدالله-ابن-خردادبه&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Abu ’l-Qāsim ʿUbayd Allāh b. ʿAbd Allāh Ibn Khurdādhbih (ca. 820/825–912) ابوالقاسم عبیدالله عبدالله ابن خردادبه&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#abu-l-q%c4%81sim-%ca%bfubayd-all%c4%81h-b-%ca%bfabd-all%c4%81h-ibn-khurd%c4%81dhbih-ca-820825912-%d8%a7%d8%a8%d9%88%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%82%d8%a7%d8%b3%d9%85-%d8%b9%d8%a8%db%8c%d8%af%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%84%d9%87-%d8%b9%d8%a8%d8%af%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%84%d9%87-%d8%a7%d8%a8%d9%86-%d8%ae%d8%b1%d8%af%d8%a7%d8%af%d8%a8%d9%87&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;kitāb-almasālik-walmamālik-the-book-of-roads-and-kingdoms-كتاب-المسالك-والممالك-ca-870&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;em&gt;Kitāb al‑Masālik wa‑l‑Mamālik (The Book of Roads and Kingdoms) كتاب المسالك والممالك&lt;/em&gt; ca. 870&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#kit%c4%81b-almas%c4%81lik-walmam%c4%81lik-the-book-of-roads-and-kingdoms-%d9%83%d8%aa%d8%a7%d8%a8-%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%85%d8%b3%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%83-%d9%88%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%85%d9%85%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%83-ca-870&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The follwing is the section describing the maritime route to the East, from the Persian Gulf to China, including Southeast Asia and the islands of the Indian Ocean.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
